description: Live performances from local and national artists across multiple genres including rock, jazz, folk, and electronic music. This day-long festival features three stages with continuous performances, food trucks offering cuisines from around the world, craft beer gardens, artisan market stalls, and interactive art installations. Family-friendly activities will be available in the designated kids' zone, including face painting and instrument-making workshops. Early bird tickets are available now with special discounts for students, seniors, and groups of 5 or more people.
title: Summer Music Festival
